Indeed is building an AI-powered future that keeps people at the center.
Hannah Calhoon, Vice President of AI at Indeed, explains how the company is helping teams embrace technology without losing the human touch. Indeed is developing flexible AI systems that can handle repetitive tasks — freeing employees to focus on creativity, decision-making, and making a real impact.

From engineering to marketing, Indeed empowers every department to use AI intentionally by enhancing human potential.

description:

In this third and final episode of The Inspiration Lab, Amazon Ads Global Director of Brand Marketing, Carly Zipp, sits down with Jill Cress, CMO and CXO of H&R Block, to discuss measurement in marketing and innovating for a legacy brand. Jill and Carly recap H&R Block’s recent full-funnel campaign with Amazon Ads, discuss the winning combination of storytelling and performance marketing, and examine the continued convergence of entertainment and commerce.
